### 1) สร้าง Guest ใหม่ (เคสรันผ่าน)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/guests
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Nattapong",
  "phone": "0812345678",
  "email": "nattapong@example.com",
  "address": "Bangkok, Thailand"
}

### 2) เคสไม่ผ่าน (ไม่มี name)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/guests
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "0812345678"
}

### 3) ดึงทั้งหมด
GET http://localhost:3000/api/guests

### 4) ดึงตาม id
GET http://localhost:3000/api/guests/1

### 5) แก้ไขข้อมูล (PUT)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/guests/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Nattapong Edited",
  "phone": "0899999999",
  "email": "newmail@example.com",
  "address": "Chiang Mai"
}

### 6) ลบ
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/guests/1
